XFINITY.TV V0.1
===============

This is an application for Boxee to watch shows in http://www.fancast.com

INSTALLATION
============

Copy the directory app and rename it to xfinity in the user apps directory of
your Boxee. That is:

- Linux: ~/.boxee/UserData/apps/
- Mac OS/X: ~/Library/Application Support/BOXEE/UserData/apps/
- AppleTV: ~/Library/Application\ Support/BOXEE/UserData/apps/
- Windows Vista: C:\Users\<windows user name>\AppData\Roaming\BOXEE\userdata\apps\
- Windows XP: C:\Documents and Settings\<your windows user name>\Application Data\BOXEE\userdata\apps\
